casebody.data:
Breidenbach, Appellant, v. Importers’ & Traders’ Nat. Bank, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by Rudolph A. Breidenbach against the Importers’ & Traders’ National Bank.

. Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion granted, with $10 costs.
